data.description: If you're looking for the primary room on the main floor, this home is for you!  Two additional bedrooms are located upstairs offering a little quiet time for the homeowner.  Add a couple of rocking chairs and relax on the covered front porch.  The home is within minutes of Columbia's International Corridor, shopping and dining.  The home backs up to a wooded area and is walking distance to the neighborhood park.
